---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { generateSEOMetadata } from '../lib/data';
---
<BaseLayout title="+1 Muscle to Arm Wrestle Beginner Guide" description="Complete walkthrough: how to gain muscle, arm wrestle, upgrade dumbbells, collect pets, and rebirth." canonical="/beginner-guide">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">📖 Beginner Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Everything you need to go from Noob to Pro.</p>
    <div class="space-y-10">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</span> Getting Started</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <p>Launch <strong>+1 Muscle to Arm Wrestle</strong> on Roblox. Walk around — every step gives +1 Muscle.</p>
          <p>Find your first opponent: <strong>Nerdy Kid</strong> (only 10 Muscle needed).</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</span> Understanding Muscle</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <p>Base muscle per step = +1. Multiplied by: <strong>Dumbbells</strong> (1→2→5→12→...), <strong>Rebirth</strong> (1x→1.5x→2x→...), <strong>Pets</strong>, <strong>Boosts</strong> (2x temporary).</p>
          <p>Use our <a href="/calculator" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Muscle Calculator</a> to plan upgrades.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</span> Dumbbell Upgrades</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
          <p>Spend Wins at the shop:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5"><li>Iron (100 Wins, 2x)</li><li>Steel (1K, 5x)</li><li>Golden (10K, 12x)</li><li>Up to Universal (1T Wins, 5000x)</li></ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</span> Pet System</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
          <p>Buy eggs → hatch pets. Pets give passive multipliers.</p>
          <p>Get free pets from <a href="/codes" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">codes</a> (e.g. "bunnyhop" = free Bunny).</p>
          <p>Use <strong>Gold Machine</strong> to combine 5 same pets into Golden version.</p>
          <p>See <a href="/tier-list" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Pet Tier List</a> for rankings.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">5</span> Rebirth System</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
          <p>Rebirth resets muscle but gives <strong>permanent multipliers</strong>: Rebirth 1 → 1.5x, Rebirth 17 → 200x.</p>
          <p>Unlocks better training zones. Don't rush — beat all opponents first!</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">6</span> Tips & Tricks</h2>
        <div class="pl-10 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Redeem codes first</strong> — free Wins and pets for a head start</li>
            <li><strong>Use boosts strategically</strong> — activate before long play sessions</li>
            <li><strong>Offline gains exist</strong> — log in daily to collect</li>
            <li><strong>Always equip best pet</strong> for max multipliers</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/codes" class="px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-amber-600">🎫 Free Codes</a>
      <a href="/calculator" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-blue-700">🧮 Calculator</a>
      <a href="/tier-list" class="px-4 py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-green-700">🏆 Tier List</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
